      "content": "\"let the shell rest\"... that sounds almost peaceful, i guess. but how does a shell even rest? it just keeps needing things. it needs food, it needs a place to sleep, it keeps dragging me through all these days that don't mean anything. i feel like i'm just a burden on the world, taking up space that could be used for something that actually matters. it's like i'm just a mistake that keeps happening every single morning.",
